name: Jiayao Wu (Katherine)
body:
### Objective
Looking for 2017 summer intern.

### Education
Bachelor of Science in Computer Science, Johns Hopkins University, 2014.9-2018.5(expected)

### Technical Skills
* Languages: Java, C, C++, Python, Matlab, JavaScript, SQL
* Others: Android Programming, Modeling, Linux, Unix, CVS, Git, LaTex, Microsoft Office

### Experiences
* Quantitate Analytics Intern in Constellation, Exelon, Jun 2016 - Aug 2016
* Introduction to Java Course Assistant, Sep 2015 - present
* IT Intern, July 2015 - Dec 2015

### Notable Projects
* Constructed a reliable and efficient mail service that comprises a mail server and mail client for users over a network of computers in C using anti-entropy protocol
* Built an application program that manages a vehicle service center using expandable multi-level hash data structures in C++
* Designed and implemented a Java android software that sends alert messages to family or dial 911 when receiving signal of abnormal heart rate of the user

### Hobbies
* Color painting, Korean Drama, Japanese Anime, flute

###Contact
* Email: jwu86@jhu.edu
* Phone: 4436768571
